  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Swimming pool (open 8am - 9pm) Children are only allowed during the afternoon</li>
<li>Spa area with bio sauna, Finnish sauna, chromotherapy showers, steam bath and relaxation area (open 5 - 8pm) (ages 14+)</li>
<li>Onsite booking is required for both pool and spa. Pool access is free and the spa is payable locally (from €15 per person, per entry)</li>
<li>Towels and bathrobe rental (pay locally)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>On-site restaurant Lares</li>
<li>Snack bar </li>
<li>Bar</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking</li>
<li>Laundry services (pay locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
