  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Apartments </strong>are around 30<span>m²</span> sleeping two to four people. This apartment has <span>a living room with a double sofa bed, a separate area with a double bed, a fully-equipped kitchenette, balcony and bathroom with shower.</span></p>
<p><strong>Standard One Bedroom Apartment </strong>are around 41<span>m²</span> sleeping two to five people. <span>This apartment has a double room with a private bathroom, a living room with a double fold-away wall bed and a single bed, a fully-equipped kitchenette and an additional bathroom with shower.</span></p>
<p>One linen set with towels and bedding is provided per person per week, with a mid-week towel change. End of stay cleaning is included, except the kitchenette.</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Living area with sofa bed</li>
<li>Well equipped kitchenette with two cooking rings</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bathroom with shower </li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Microwaves can be rented locally (approx.€35 per week)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
